---
/* FAQSection.astro */
---

<section
  id="faq"
  data-allow-scroll
  class="w-full bg-transparent text-gray-100 py-24"
>
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Preguntas frecuentes
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Resolvemos las dudas más comunes sobre nuestras landing pages y el CRM.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ items -->
    <div class="space-y-4 pb-32">
      <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6 transition-all open:bg-white/10">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between font-medium">
          <span>¿Qué incluye una landing page?</span>
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Diseño moderno, copy optimizado, mobile first y conexión con formularios o CRM.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6 transition-all open:bg-white/10">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between font-medium">
          <span>¿Están optimizadas para conversiones?</span>
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Sí, usamos UX/UI, CTA claros y performance optimizada.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6 transition-all open:bg-white/10">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between font-medium">
          <span>¿Qué es el CRM?</span>
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Una plataforma para gestionar leads, clientes y ventas.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6 transition-all open:bg-white/10">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between font-medium">
          <span>¿El CRM es personalizable?</span>
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Pipelines, automatizaciones, reportes y roles de usuario.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6 transition-all open:bg-white/10">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between font-medium">
          <span>¿Landing y CRM se integran?</span>
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Cada lead entra automáticamente al CRM.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
